open server manager > manage > add roles and features > next
> role based/feature based > next > choose the server and next >
click the box for Web server IIS and next > click SMTP server > next > install > wait to finish

go to admin powershell, type:
iisreset


server manager > tools > internet information services iis 6.0 manager


under the pc name you will se that SMTP has been installed. make sure its running.


